          <p>The El Dorado Casitas Royale is our pick for the perfect all-inclusive    in the Riviera Maya area, just 40 minutes South   of Cancun. This resort is for adults only and is perfect for those   couples searching for something secluded and intimate. Looking left or   right from the white sand beach, all you will see is more beach, quite a   contrast from the hotel zone offered in Cancun. The casitas are unique - Romantic features include a jacuzzi overlooking the ocean in every room, bed on   the balcony, guaranteed king size bed, and my favorite the agua del a'more - an outdoor shower surrounded by stone but open to the sky. The spa offers a water journey circuit including jets, jacuzzis, cold plunge pools, steam room and sauna - a must before you enjoy a couples massage at the spa or beachfont (extra charge applies).All meals, drinks, activities   and tips are included in the price. When you stay in a casita, you have access to all restaurants, activities and areas at the Eldorado Royale resort next door. To see some of the activities available, see our pictures for the Eldorado Royale. When you are ready to take in the   sights of Cancun or Playa del Carmen, there is a  shuttle for your convenience. Free weddings are also offered - call to discuss options and qualifications. </p>
